    "C001": [
      {
        "type": "message",
        "user": "U015",
        "text": "Heads up \u2014 Deal #10057 (Flores, Stock #N16028) has a gross variance. The approved desk recap from Derek Loomis shows $7,500 total gross but the deal_log has it at $6,700. Escalating to Marcus per the high-gross override.",
